# Project Detail Pages Enhancement

## Overview
Current tabs show connection strings but NO guidance. Each service tab needs: "What is this?", "When to use it?", Quick integration code, SDK installation, Connection details. This reduces friction and helps developers understand each service.

## Technical Approach
Enhance each service tab in project detail page with explanation sections. Add "What is this?" section, quick integration code examples, SDK installation instructions, use case guidance, link to full docs. Make code examples copy-pasteable.

## User Stories

### US-001: Create Service Tab Template
**Priority:** 1
**Maven Steps:** [5, 10]
**MCP Tools:** []

As a UI developer, I want a reusable service tab template so that all service tabs have consistent structure.

**Acceptance Criteria:**
- ServiceTab component created
- Sections: Overview, Quick Start, Connection Details, Docs Link
- Consistent layout across all tabs
- Typecheck passes

**Status:** false

### US-002: Enhance Database Tab
**Priority:** 1
**Maven Steps:** [5, 10]
**MCP Tools:** []

As a developer, I want database tab guidance so that I understand how to use the database service.

**Acceptance Criteria:**
- "What is the Database Service?" section
- PostgreSQL-powered data with auto-generated REST & GraphQL APIs
- "When to use it" section
- Quick integration: npm install nextmavens-js
- Code example: client initialization and query
- Connection details: database URL
- Link to full docs
- Typecheck passes

**Status:** false

